%% 3.2.3 Edit Profile / Upload Avatar — sequence
%% POST /api/Upload/Image multipart → Cloudinary
%% Note: User entity has no AvatarUrl yet; persist URL via User extension or Student-only flow
%% BR11: Client limits 5MB + standard image formats

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Guardian as Guardian
    participant App as Mobile App
    participant UC as UploadController
    participant CLD as CloudinaryService
    participant Cloud as Cloudinary

    Guardian->>App: Change avatar — gallery or camera
    App->>App: Validate size/format (BR11)
    App->>UC: POST /api/Upload/Image multipart
    UC->>CLD: UploadImageAsync(file)
    CLD->>Cloud: Upload
    Cloud-->>CLD: URL
    UC-->>App: 200 OK + imageUrl
    App->>Guardian: Refresh avatar (PUT /api/User/Update if backend supports avatar field)
